    "title": "脱・無難論",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、トレーニングメニューを考えるため\r\n図書室にやってきたのだが……。",
            "enText": "One day, I came to the library \nto think of a training menu…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "pathId": -6096348317805517326,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……いや、これも無難だな。",
            "enText": "… No, it's also safe.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 53,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "悩み事？",
                    "enText": "Worries?",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -5392745321628423524
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": 15244076570875076
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4881355278645050740,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "ああ、私は何事も無難に行動する傾向がある。\r\nレースにしろ、トレーニングにしろ、な。",
            "enText": "Yes, I tend to take everything in stride. \nWhether it's racing or training.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -2311655344217773639
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": 1838737683554181410
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 669463563734974088,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "雨が降れば同じ運動量を室内で行い。\r\n疲労がたまれば予定をずらして休養に充てる。",
            "enText": "If it rains, we do the same amount of \nexercise indoors. If it rains, the same \namount of exercise is done indoors, and if \nthey are tired, the schedule is shifted to \nallow them to rest.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -5435405359726288330
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -3492020459960809792
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5551445382633939657,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "無難に論理立てれば推論は容易い。その点、\r\nリスクを積んだ先は善かれ悪しかれ未知数だ。",
            "enText": "It's easy to reason in a safe and logical \nway. On the other hand, the risks involved \nare, for better or worse, unknowable.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 48,
                    "pathId": 7730733457282883686
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 85,
                    "pathId": 4710529809215441213
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 602397301364061508,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……で、あれば。推論の幅を広げるためにも、\r\n多少のリスクを負う価値はあると考え至った。",
            "enText": "At… if you will. We thought it was worth \ntaking a few risks to broaden our reasoning.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 42,
                    "pathId": -4250819423443403505
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -5557509437017339981
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3686409633667825108,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "それで、ケガの無いようダートコースでの\r\nトレーニングを想定し、プランを練ったが――",
            "enText": "So we planned to train on a dirt \ntrack to avoid injury…",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": 6135495302212292614
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": 1130266825766757508
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2441242243776981957,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……気づいてしまったんだ。\r\nこれこそ無難な行動そのものだと！",
            "enText": "I've just realised… This is \nthe safest thing to do!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "頭で考えるより、行動あるのみ",
                    "enText": "Don't think, just act!",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ケガをしたら元も子もない",
                    "enText": "If you get injured, there's \nnothing you can do.",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": -4814561841676673746
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 2041228835113489601
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5787617140500584909,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "頭だと？　それは私の頭が――あ。",
            "enText": "Your head? It's my head—oh.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 55,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": -6807718805659338662
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": 5854620774845610009
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5481516885373826835,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……はぁ。\r\nまたやってしまった……。",
            "enText": "… Huh. I've done it again…",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 57,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 737388342405608750
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -1524229309823577204
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3396652502781191751,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "『頭』というワードを聞くと、その、\r\n頭の大きさをいじられている気がして……。",
            "enText": "When I hear the word \"head\" I feel like I'm \nbeing teased about the size of my head…",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 70,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": -4712772355813510811
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 1875209771672483065
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3583959521263763890,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "すまない。行動しなければ、\r\n机上の空論だと君は言いたいのだろう？",
            "enText": "I'm sorry. If we don't act, we're talking \nout of our asses, aren't we?",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -6972909931295928282
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -6147925890003346148
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4932908169060978217,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "考えるより行動しろ……なるほど、\r\n確かに無茶らしいと言えばそうかもしれない。",
            "enText": "Don't just think about it, act about it. … \nWell, that sounds absurd, doesn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 70,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 7651883035378201858
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": -6564550543256374276
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1866050699725970017,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "ありがとう。\r\n何かつかめた気がするよ。",
            "enText": "Thank you. I think I'm getting \nthe hang of this.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -2349201205013402511
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 2504651526048764119
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5070146053413191971,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "……つまり、無難でいいという事か？\r\n君が言うのならばそうなのだろう。",
            "enText": "… So you're saying it's safe? If \nyou say so, then I guess so.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": 2333117600949328821
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 4308675663830761643
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7832968457485059708,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "ふむ……であれば、このトレーニング論も\r\n無駄ではないという事か。",
            "enText": "Hmmm… so this training \ntheory is not in vain.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": -5925766725360314402
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": -8254173656166835819
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5951447877317507626,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "そうだ、よければ私の考えた\r\nトレーニング論を見てもらえないだろうか？",
            "enText": "Yes, if you'd like to have a look \nat my theory of training.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": -2410781264425185395
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 6341025088846296121
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2570766124185376851,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "Biwa Hayahide",
            "jpText": "『多少無茶ができる安全なトレーニング論』\r\n……というんだが。",
            "enText": "It's called \"The Theory of Safe Training for \nthe Somewhat Reckless\"…",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": 4104038149452458568
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": 8804470642578484890
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -7202765920023370250
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5129563382943215586,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女のトレーニング論を見せてもらった。\r\n安全で効率的……とても無難なものであった。",
            "enText": "She showed me her training theory. It was \nsafe, efficient… and very safe.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
